In comparing the two at ql151 I noticed that the parry stick had better damage, better adds to evades, and a higher crit. The only thing I noticed was the attack speed. <br>
2.5/3.5 for the stick vs  1.2/2.0 for the claw.<br>
I was wondering what thoughts you folks may have on this. <br>
What physical init would you need to take the parry stick to the same speed as claws.<br>
